OL,3,CGPs in Wales blocked from prescribing
OL,4,Cweight loss drugs due to huge demand
OL,6,FGPs will continue to be blocked from
OL,7,Fprescribing weight loss drugs by the
OL,8,FWelsh Government because NHS Wales is
OL,9,Fnot ready for the huge demand.
OL,11,FAround 186,000 people in Wales are
OL,12,Festimated to be eligible for
OL,13,Ftirzepatide (Mounjaro) alone, which
OL,14,Fhas been approved by the National
OL,15,FInstitute for Health and Care
OL,16,FExcellence (NICE) for managing obesity.
OL,18,FBut people can only currently be
OL,19,Fprescribed the medication through a
OL,20,Fspecialist service rather than through
OL,21,FGP practices.
