OL,3,CGPs in Wales blocked from prescribing
OL,4,Cweight loss drugs due to huge demand
OL,6,FA rollout to include GPs has been
OL,7,Fpaused while a new "clinical pathway"
OL,8,Fis developed, due to fears the Welsh
OL,9,FNHS cannot currently handle this level
OL,10,Fof demand.
OL,12,FAn exception exists for a small number
OL,13,Fof high-need patients who, for
OL,14,Fexample, have cancer, need a
OL,15,Ftransplant or are in the care of
OL,16,Ffertility services.
