OL,3,CGPs in Wales blocked from prescribing
OL,4,Cweight loss drugs due to huge demand
OL,6,FSioned Rees, interim director of
OL,7,FPublic Health, and Andrew Evans, the
OL,8,FWelsh Government's Chief
OL,9,FPharmaceutical Officer, issued an
OL,10,Fupdate to health boards today (October
OL,11,F23).
OL,13,FThe specialist-only rule also applies
OL,14,Fto semaglutide (Wegovy) and
OL,15,Fliraglutide (Saxenda), two other
OL,16,Fweight loss drugs, with a global surge
OL,17,Fin demand far outstripping supply.
