OL,3,CGPs in Wales blocked from prescribing
OL,4,Cweight loss drugs due to huge demand
OL,6,FAnyone already receiving these drugs
OL,7,Fon the NHS before the circular was
OL,8,Fpublished can continue their treatment
OL,9,Fand will not have their prescriptions
OL,10,Fstopped. The update does not apply to
OL,11,Fprescribing tirzepatide for its other
OL,12,Flicensed uses.
OL,14,FWelsh Government officials wrote: "The
OL,15,Fnew model will include the development
OL,16,Fof a clinical pathway with the aims of
OL,17,Ftreating and managing obesity as a
OL,18,Fchronic, recurring condition and to
OL,19,Fsupport equitable access to weight-
OL,20,Floss drugs and associated wrap-around
OL,21,Fsupport."
