OL,6,FNICE usually requires a new drug to be
OL,7,Favailable within two months but
OL,8,Fgranted an exemption, extending the
OL,9,Fimplementation period to up to 12
OL,10,Fyears, in recognition of the
OL,11,Fpotentially very large eligible cohort.
OL,13,FThe officials wrote: "We appreciate
OL,14,Fconsiderable demand for specialist
OL,15,Fweight management services and a
OL,16,Fgrowing pressure for access to these
OL,17,Fmedications through the NHS.
