OL,6,F"The work being undertaken to develop
OL,7,Fa new clinical pathway will support
OL,8,Fbuilding capacity and capability
OL,9,Facross Wales across specialist,
OL,10,Fprimary care and community settings.
OL,12,F"These pathways will ensure
OL,13,Ftirzepatide and other weight-loss
OL,14,Fmedications can be made available in
OL,15,Fthe NHS in Wales in a seamless,
OL,16,Fequitable, safe and effective way."
